<div class="careerwrpr">
	<p>Golden Software's corporate office is located in the heart of downtown Golden at 809 14th Street, adjacent to the Colorado School of Mines campus. The company currently employs seventeen people. We look for quality individuals that will help us represent Golden Software as the leader in our industry. We expect a high level of integrity that our customers have come to expect from Golden Software. We are an innovative employer, offering employees competitive salaries, outstanding work conditions, and exciting technical challenges.</p>
