	</h4>
	<p><strong>What are we looking for?</strong>
	</p>
	<p>Golden Software is seeking a full-time customer support engineer to provide top-notch support for our scientific visualization and mapping applications. We are looking for a self-motivated, passionate individual who truly cares about what is best for the customer.</p>
	<h5><strong>What we offer: </strong>
	</h5>
	<ul>
