		<li>Stability – Golden Software has been in business for more than 30 years. Most of our team has worked here for over 10 years.</li>
	</ul>
	<h5><strong>What we do:</strong>
	</h5>
	<p>We develop, sell, and support the best geoscience visualization software. We are very proud of our products and invite you to download the demos and see for yourself.</p>
	<h5><strong>What you’ll do:</strong>
	</h5>
	<p>You will support all six Golden Software products. You will be responsible for providing phone, email, and LiveChat support to customers who come from a wide variety of industries. In addition to solving the customer concerns, you also teach the customer how to use the product more efficiently and effectively.</p>
	<p>In addition to customer support, you will also play a direct role in the future product development. A critical piece of customer support is relaying customer feedback on to our development team. You will have a firsthand look into the product release cycle as you’ll be responsible for testing products and providing feedback as necessary.</p>
	<p>As with any thriving company, we have a slew of side-projects and opportunities for anyone to tackle. No two days are alike here at Golden Software.</p>
